# Post-Development Workflow

After completing any development task:

1. Run the app locally and verify the changes work
2. Run existing tests and confirm they pass
3. **Never modify existing tests that previously passed** — only update them if file names or imports changed
4. Write e2e tests covering the new feature end-to-end
5. Ensure all tests pass and coverage is above 95%
6. Only then commit and push to GitHub
